snippet.title: Just Read The Instructions Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
JUST READ THE INSTRUCTIONS is a surreal co-op first person shooter game where the only thing that matters is following the next set of instructions. Enemies will flood the scene, your weapons will break, more instructions will come, and then repeat.

Aspire to not die.

Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1461370/Just_Read_The_Instructions/

Or follow us on twitter for updates about the game: https://twitter.com/TheKnackelibang
